@startuml
title 控制权状态机
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Observer
Observer --> PendingGrant : Claim
PendingGrant --> Controller : Grant
PendingGrant --> Rejected : Reject
Rejected --> Observer
Controller --> Controller : Renew
Controller --> Preempting : Preempt
Preempting --> Revoked : 被抢占
Preempting --> Controller : 抢占成功
Controller --> Released : Release
Controller --> Revoked : Lease Expired
Released --> Observer
Revoked --> Observer
@enduml
